      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEWANA FAMILY (3) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (29.91) at The Meadows in a Special conditions H. Lines up from box 3 for the first time. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can find winning form. DAPPER CHAP (8) failed to feature last start after being shuffled back early at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 4 lengths at Ballarat (24.85) beating Electrojet in a Mix 3/4 on June 24. Form from his last run is proving strong. Should be thereabouts. BISCOTTINO (5) has a strong winning strike-rate over this journey with three wins and a placing from seven tries. Was out of placings last time (30.43) at The Meadows in a Special conditions H, finishing fourth and beaten 2 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. IAN ALBERT (1) scored by half a length last time (26.17) in a Mix 3/4 over 460m at Warragul. Has two wins already from this draw.",
